{"type":"message","id":"0de2dfa2","parentId":"19926be2","timestamp":"2026-04-29T07:02:45.639Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-04-29 03:00 EDT] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Decision Made: **Keep qwen2.5-coder:7b** as backup; **Use qwen3:4b as primary** for coding on Bobby's Mac; qwen3:4b is newer architecture, more efficient, 4B parameters = ~3-4GB RAM usage\n- Next Step: Test qwen3:4b when download completes; Verify it runs well on 8GB MacBook Air; Consider integrating with Cody for coding tasks\n- Reflections: Theme: `reflections` kept surfacing across 248 memories.; confidence: 1.00; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:18-21, memory/2026-04-10.md:22-25, memory/2026-04-10.md:26-29; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `memory/2026-04-10.md` kept surfacing across 238 memories.; confidence: 1.00; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:43-46, memory/2026-04-10.md:47-50, memory/2026-04-10.md:51-54; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `1.00` kept surfacing across 162 memories.; confidence: 0.85; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:18-21, memory/2026-04-10.md:22-25, memory/2026-04-10.md:26-29; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `22-25` kept surfacing across 153 memories.; confidence: 0.80; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:43-46, memory/2026-04-10.md:47-50, memory/2026-04-10.md:51-54; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `26-29` kept surfacing across 153 memories.; confidence: 0.80; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:43-46, memory/2026-04-10.md:47-50, memory/2026-04-10.md:51-54; note: reflection\n- Reflections: Theme: `18-21` kept surfacing across 152 memories.; confidence: 0.79; evidence: memory/2026-04-10.md:43-46, memory/2026-04-10.md:47-50, memory/2026-04-10.md:51-54; note: reflection\n- qwen2.5-coder:7b - Installed: Downloaded and installed (4.7GB); Bobby was concerned it's too heavy for his 8GB MacBook Air\n- Reflections: Theme: `1.00` kept surfacing across 150 memories.; confidence: 0.86; evidence: memory/